[
  {
    "startTime": 9.84,
    "endTime": 12.16,
    "text": "Oh, Harry, Thank goodness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.16,
    "endTime": 14.69,
    "text": "We hoped you'd only gone one grate too far."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.72,
    "endTime": 16.560000000000002,
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, Mr. Gilderoy Lockhart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.94,
    "endTime": 28.490000000000002,
    "text": "Mum fancies him. Make way there. Please! Let me by, madam."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.5,
    "endTime": 29.1,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.2,
    "endTime": 30.4,
    "text": "Excuse me, little girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.52,
    "endTime": 31.88,
    "text": "This is for the Daily Prophet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.61,
    "endTime": 39.78,
    "text": "It can't be- Harry Potter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.24,
    "endTime": 42.13,
    "text": "Harry Potter!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.34,
    "endTime": 43.78,
    "text": "Excuse me, madam."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.54,
    "endTime": 47.48,
    "text": "Nice big smile, Harry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.48,
    "endTime": 49.099999999999994,
    "text": "Together you and I rate the front page."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.54,
    "endTime": 51.35,
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, what an extraordinary moment this is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.35,
    "endTime": 72.42,
    "text": "When young Harry stepped into Flourish and Blotts this morning to purchase my autobiography, Magical Me, which, incidentally, is currently celebrating its 27th week atop the Daily Prophet bestseller list,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.17,
    "endTime": 90.45,
    "text": "he had no idea that he would, in fact, be leaving with my entire collected works free of charge. Now ladies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.99,
    "endTime": 93.11999999999999,
    "text": "Harry, now you give me those,"
  },
  {
